task.summary: Added basic oscillator functionality with gain and H0 sliders.
Added glottal flow waveform plot, and cosine Rosenberg glottal model. Broke down App.js into multiple components.
Added vocal tract filter and fixed the audio processing for filter cascading.
Added help tooltips for each component. Added a preset system to centralize all synth setting data.
Added more presets and a preset selector.
Better noise formula (pink noise and polynomial curve w.r.t Oq)
Changed filter algorithm yet again, added formant gains. Fixed source being set before params are set. Changed up the presets.
Dedicated components for graph plotting. Adjusted presets again.
Longer transition phase for filter parameters
Reverted changes to LF model. Using limits and normalization to prevent issues.
Reverted changes to LF model. Using limits and normalization to prevent issues.
Reverted changes to LF model. Using limits and normalization to prevent issues.
Added plot of vocal tract frequency response.
Changed update order for vocal tract parameters.
Updated LF model to add asymmetry parameter. Reduced beating occurring with aspiration noise.
Added a rough (and very laggy) interactive 2d vowel space graph for F1 and F2
